AULA 1|O3DE:
Pais: EUA
Requisitos minimos:
•	Windows 10 64-bit version 1809 or Ubuntu 20.04 LTS
•	Quad-core Intel or AMD processor, 2.5 GHz or faster
•	8 GB RAM
•	DirectX 12, Vulkan-compatible, or Metal-compatible video card with 2 GB VRAM minimum
o	4 GB VRAM recommended
o	NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 or better, driver version 471.11 or later recommended
o	AMD Radeon Pro 560 or better
o	Intel HD 630 or better
o	Shader Model 6.2 (or Shader Model 6.3 to use raytracing features)
•	40 - 100 GB of free disk space
•	1366 x 768 px screen resolution
2D/3D: Apenas 3D 
